				<td colspan="2"><span>I agree with Corgar, MS is a good place to learn to AoE kite.  After swarming for the last few levels, I am about to enter Nadox and try AoE kiting.  This scares the he!!  out of me, for loss of xp.  Trust me, I will be practicing before I enter Nadox.
<br />

<br />
Couple things, you might want to try to help with lag.  First, turn off all spell effects.  Second, cut your clip plane down to 50% and last, if you are playing at 1280x1024, try turning it down to 800x600 and lowering the graphic details.  All of these help, everything is a blurr anyway, since you are going to be running in a circle, who cares what the blurr looks like!!  
<br />

<br />
Best of luck!!</span></td>
